messages.message:
There is a new bug that got introduced recently
When you run an app from the hub, it goes to app page instead of app runs page
For example, in my case, it went to
https://aihub-sandbox.internal.instabase.com/hub/apps/ae4f013c-4d98-44f4-97d4-01e8ed66fe7f/Doc-Summarization
instead of
https://aihub-sandbox.internal.instabase.com/hub/apps/ae4f013c-4d98-44f4-97d4-01e8ed66fe7f/runs
